{"tid":224734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"問世間情是何物 咩叫愛","createTime":"2017-05-01T09:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T22:43:50.000Z","uid":50195,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"994c6e5c7135eee8766c134fac66960ccb8bc395","tid":224734,"uid":50195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"利申返先我係藍絲<br />\n我自己係會勁投入 乜都為對方諗一餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對方係相反 中意自由多d 但佢又對我好好既 又唔係唔愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想知大家會點表達愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d703e01210f9e5cda46fdf7cf113fe92b3617b","tid":224734,"uid":50195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:48:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc4c23534ddf9314e25aaed44d60d2524623323","tid":224734,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申返先我係<span style=\"color: red;\">藍絲</span><br />\n我自己係會勁投入 乜都為對方諗一餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對方係相反 中意自由多d 但佢又對我好好既 又唔係唔愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想知大家會點表達愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲你老母"},{"pid":"9408270708246303ba55fa0bc2ab99f43b9b136d","tid":224734,"uid":103212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:50:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70aeff8677b199fcf9c441ceb1aceb4ff04c8f30","tid":224734,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6c3c3c8395e482dcddbdbe29750ee1fb3ef3d5","tid":224734,"uid":50195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申返先我係藍絲<br />\n我自己係會勁投入 乜都為對方諗一餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對方係相反 中意自由多d 但佢又對我好好既 又唔係唔愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想知大家會點表達愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個個人表達方法都唔同嫁啦 我個FD對佢條女冷冷淡淡咁<br />\n<br />\n平時佢條女出街去邊佢都唔問多句 佢條女成日都覺得佢太冷淡<br />\n<br />\n但同我個FD出街佢成日都剩係記得條女叫佢返屋企前買咩俾佢食<br />\n<br />\n又間唔中拎電話出黎睇下佢有冇打黎OR WS 佢<br />\n<br />\n不過佢平時無表現出黎或者唔識表達姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呀好sweet呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼會記得女朋友 我個個一玩就唔記得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我都覺個個表達方式好唔同 所以都未理由逼佢變既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0369bec024b2ea7968a09fa3905242a8b2c6fd9","tid":224734,"uid":50195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申返先我係<span style=\"color: red;\">藍絲</span><br />\n我自己係會勁投入 乜都為對方諗一餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對方係相反 中意自由多d 但佢又對我好好既 又唔係唔愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想知大家會點表達愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲你老母</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213bbaf7708ac66236fa4380ac5f3bb1d2c26f4c","tid":224734,"uid":50195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>利申返先我係藍絲<br />\n我自己係會勁投入 乜都為對方諗一餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對方係相反 中意自由多d 但佢又對我好好既 又唔係唔愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想知大家會點表達愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個個人表達方法都唔同嫁啦 我個FD對佢條女冷冷淡淡咁<br />\n<br />\n平時佢條女出街去邊佢都唔問多句 佢條女成日都覺得佢太冷淡<br />\n<br />\n但同我個FD出街佢成日都剩係記得條女叫佢返屋企前買咩俾佢食<br />\n<br />\n又間唔中拎電話出黎睇下佢有冇打黎OR WS 佢<br />\n<br />\n不過佢平時無表現出黎或者唔識表達姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呀好sweet呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼會記得女朋友 我個個一玩就唔記得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我都覺個個表達方式好唔同 所以都<span style=\"color: red;\">無</span>理由逼佢變既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a221fc70e5d3b7302c5b9774f6f38b0117a0f1da","tid":224734,"uid":59114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:54:55.000Z","msg":"愛只有簡單筆劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，卻比想像複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024d79fc273ecba33c8c7e84afd23c2f4fecb8d8","tid":224734,"uid":50195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你好 起左起你底<br />\n你而家仲有無事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3db0196e30bf1f742fd96b7c4d6eeb7a0f77b6","tid":224734,"uid":50195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:57:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛只有簡單筆劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，卻比想像複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打好文采<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都唔知係人複雜定愛複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能愛可以好簡單"},{"pid":"3d85323069cc12b8cfcce2a4d5fac4b366b73dcf","tid":224734,"uid":28277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:15:27.